These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, iced-tea, almond-milk, milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, weightlifting, tennis, golf
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not the person who's sport is lacrosse##6
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not the person drinking almond-milk##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | milk    | tea    | almond-milk |
| Sport      | golf | lacrosse | tennis | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, 7up, juice
There 4 different types of food: lime, cucumber, cherry, corn
1. the person eating lime is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
3. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
4. the person drinking cola is not the person eating cucumber##6
5. the person eating corn is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person eating lime is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
7. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
8. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | cola  | 7up    | fanta | juice    |
| Food       | corn | cucumber | cherry  | lime |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, milk, almond-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, freelancer, lawyer, scientist
1. the person drinking almond-milk is not the videographer##6
2. the freelancer is not the person drinking milk##6
3. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
4. the freelancer is the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the freelancer##1
6. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
7. the videographer is on the far left or far right##3
8. the lawyer is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk       | soy-milk  | 7up  | milk |
| Job        | lawyer | scientist | freelancer | videographer  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, bird, hamster, frog
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, roller, taxi, bike
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
2. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
3. the person driving the bike is not the owner of the bird##6
4. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
6. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | bird | hamster | frog     | cat |
| Transport   | roller     | taxi    | scooter | bike    |

