.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, coffee, mirinda, almond-milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, scooter, helicopter, van
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
3. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
4. the person drinking coffee is not the person driving the van##6
5. the person driving the ship is not the person drinking juice##6
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | juice        | almond-milk | mirinda | coffee |
| Transport   | van | ship | scooter     | helicopter   |

