.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, romance, crime, animation
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, french, mexican, pakistani
1. the brazilian is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is not the french##6
3. the brazilian is on the far right##1
4. the french is somewhere to the right of the pakistani##5
5. the person watching crime movies is the person watching crime movies##1
6. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
7. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
8. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5
9. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | crime    | drama  | animation   |
| Nationality   | mexican  | pakistani | french | brazilian |

