.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, western, romance, mystery
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, blues, trance, pop
1. the fan trance is on the left or right of the fan indie##3
2. the fan trance is not the person watching western movies##6
3. the person watching epic movies is the fan blues##1
4. the fan indie is on the left or right of the fan pop##3
5. the fan trance is on the far left##1
6. the person watching western movies is the fan indie##1
7. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the fan indie##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | western     | romance | epic |
| Music-Genre   | trance | indie | pop      | blues         |

