The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, musician, doctor, software-developer
1. the teacher is on the left of the musician##1
2. the software-developer is somewhere to the left of the doctor##5
3. the software-developer is on the right of the musician##1
4. the musician is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the musician##3
6. the teacher is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
8. the person drinking mirinda is not the software-developer##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | mirinda  | coffee        | lemonade      | hot-chocolate          |
| Job        | teacher | musician | software-developer | doctor |

