.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, chef, videographer, analyst
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, taxi, quad-bike, jet-ski
1. the photographer is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the taxi is not the analyst##6
3. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the videographer##5
4. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is the videographer##1
7. the photographer is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
8. the chef is somewhere to the right of the analyst##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | photographer  | videographer | analyst    | chef |
| Transport   | taxi | jet-ski | quad-bike | train  |

