.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, chinchilla, bird, turtle
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, volleyball, parkour, baseball
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not the owner of the snake##6
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the owner of the bird is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
7. the person who's sport is baseball is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the bird is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | bird | snake        | turtle  | chinchilla     |
| Sport   | lacrosse     | baseball | volleyball | parkour |

