.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, board-games, cooking, singing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, funk, hip-hop, folk
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
2. the fan funk is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
3. the fan hip-hop is not the person who's hobby is cooking##6
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the fan folk and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
6. the fan funk is between the fan blues and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | cooking | board-games    | magic-tricks | singing |
| Music-Genre   | blues         | funk | folk   | hip-hop     |

