.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, grapefruit, lettuce, avocado
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, skateboard, scooter, motorbike
1. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
2. the person eating avocado is not the person driving the tram##6
3. the person driving the skateboard is the person eating avocado##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
5. the person driving the scooter is not the person eating avocado##6
6. the person eating grapefruit is not the person driving the tram##6
7. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapefruit##5
8. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | nectarine  | lettuce | grapefruit | avocado |
| Transport   | scooter | tram     | motorbike     | skateboard    |

