.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, onion, radish, zucchini
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, musical, disaster, epic
1. the person eating carrot is somewhere to the right of the person eating onion##5
2. the person eating onion is not the person watching musical movies##6
3. the person eating carrot is the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person eating radish is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5
5. the person eating carrot is between the person eating onion and the person watching documentary movies##2
6. the person eating onion is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | zucchini | onion      | carrot | radish   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | disaster | epic   | documentary |

