2. the person watching juicesy movies is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person watching drama movies is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking tea##2
4. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching juicesy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | milk       | tea | juice     | iced-tea     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | juicesy       | drama | satire |

