4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is between the security-guard and the person who's sport is swimming##2
6. the security-guard is not the person who's sport is handball##6
7. the teacher is on the right of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job     | scientist  | social-worker | teacher | security-guard |
| Sport   | handball | swimming | golf   | tennis |

