4. the owner of the frog is not the person who's hobby is camping##6
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
