3. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the van##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
6. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | soy-milk | 7up | hot-chocolate      | milk   |
| Transport   | boat  | trike   | van | helicopter |

 